{"tid":185424,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2個鐘就有GEOG 5*心態","createTime":"2017-04-03T12:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T07:30:17.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"986b1be19dd30d0f1ff9764cac126decab47c232","tid":185424,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"你只要高速GEOG技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要一堂，，足夠令你進入5*狀態！<br />\n<br />\nGEOG咁多課題，要全部背誦係無可能，而且無效率。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地著重的係點樣準備考試、點樣拆解唔同類型的問題、點樣調整心態面對考試的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n只要你有心，我就幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你建立信心，培養5*的氣量！無論遇見咩題型，你都可以對答自如。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">地理地理，健心做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\ntelegram <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FScottish_Salmon&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a9ca8cfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>( 利申： AL + CE GEOG 皆A，熱衷地理教學&amp;分享心得，希望與有心有目標的學生攜手升靚U <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) </strong>"},{"pid":"580ec52ea25a16176795ef3844e9ae2bbd579cd6","tid":185424,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"收皮啦上黎搵食仲要得5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7408b3335153d4f3a9b1ed9186ed620fa5193564","tid":185424,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"又搵水魚？"},{"pid":"257fdd3a154f5ec98cb127016b2467391b69d76a","tid":185424,"uid":95470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534ceef97b07593f15149cd4018a220ddc5460f4","tid"